    <panel_attributes>Additional constraints
--
- Inventions cannot be published unless they have at least one part.
- startMoment/endMoment must define a valid future interval when publishing.
- monthsActive = months(startMoment, endMoment), rounded to 1 decimal.
- cost = sum(part.cost). Only Euros accepted.

