    <panel_attributes>Level B additions (to be refined by owners)
--
Add: Manager, Project, Advertisement.
Project includes components: Invention, Campaign, Strategy.
Project members: 1 Project can include * Inventors, * Spokespersons, * Fundraisers. A Member is 1:1 with its Role.
Assignments: 1 Project can be assigned * Sponsorships and * AuditReports.

