    <panel_attributes>Project (Level B) - relationships (high level)
--
- managed by exactly one Manager
- includes * Inventions, * Campaigns, and * Strategies
- members (*): Inventor, Spokesperson, Fundraiser
  * members can see components even in draft mode
  * members can attach their components to projects they are involved in
- publishing a Project publishes its components automatically
- publishing a Project requires &gt;= 1 invention
- assigned * Sponsorships and * AuditReports

